ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2011-2 (Songhees First Nation)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, NO. 2011-2 (SONGHEES FIRST NATION) in order to add the name of the Songhees First Nation, the name of its governing body and the description of the lands where the Songhees First Nation goods and services tax law could apply.
